      "text": "it(\"bell behavior: pending-approval bells propagate to script+neovim, yields don't, completion bells\", async () =\u003e {\n  await withDriver",
      "contextualizedText": "// node/scripts/script-e2e.test.ts\n\nit(\"bell behavior: pending-approval bells propagate to script+neovim, yields don't, completion bells\", async () =\u003e {\n  await withDriver",
